data.text:
At last! A second Jasmine issue of the great talent of Speedy West, including the massive hit “Stratosphere Boogie”. Hear the master playing the tunes that made the steel guitar popular. This is a highly recommended purchase for both country music & steel guitar collectors.

Also available by Speedy West JASMCD3515
